## 🔧 Tech Stack

| Component | Technology | Purpose |
|-----------|-----------|---------|
| **Backend** | Spring Boot 4.0.3 | REST API framework |
| **AI Framework** | Spring AI 2.0.0-M2 | RAG pipeline, vector store integration |
| **Chat Model** | Gemma 3 (1B) via Ollama | Natural language Q&A |
| **Embeddings** | nomic-embed-text via Ollama | Semantic vector generation |
| **Vector DB** | PGVector (PostgreSQL) | Similarity search over embeddings |
| **PDF Parsing** | spring-ai-pdf-document-reader | Extract text from PDFs |
| **Frontend** | Vanilla HTML/CSS/JS | Premium dark-mode chat UI |

